data.description: Come and See! $30K in UPGRADES! Absolutely pristine and draws all the comforts of the ideal home! Owners' exquisite touches showcase a 4 bedroom, 3 bath PLUS DEN/OFFICE/GAME ROOM . A bedroom has it's own full bath! Quartz tops, tiled plank flooring, upgraded bathroom cabinets and vanity mirrors, front and back beautifully landscaped.  Feel the alluring warm welcome as you enter a wide inviting entrance into the heart of the home, an open Chef's impressive kitchen, open space to entertain your family and guests. A great location for nearby I-10 freeway, 202 South freeway, downtown Phoenix, South Mountain Regional and Estrella Mountain Parks for outdoor activities, close by shopping, schools, restaurants and more!  Be the first to call, text or email for an appt.!
